SUMMARY:Yoga / Stretch
DTSTAMP:20260702T123400Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270624T073000
DESCRIPTION:Week 4 focus: Match prep light\nGentle only — no deep static st
	retch before hard effort\n\nSession structure:\n• Breath & warm (2 min) — 
	Easy nasal breathing\, neck and shoulder rolls\n• Lower body (6 min) — Hip
	 flexor\, hamstring\, calf\, figure-4 stretch\n• Core & spine (4 min) — Ca
	t-cow\, child's pose\, gentle twist\n• Close (3 min) — Hold any tight area
	\; slow breath\n\nInstagram drill library:\n• https://www.instagram.com/re
	el/DW_zewYkeet/\n\nTheme focus: mobility\, flexibility\, recovery\, hip an
	d hamstring openness\, breath work
LOCATION:Home
DURATION:PT15M
END:VEVENT
